---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Supper Club East London | Guest Chef Dinners at The Hackney, E2" description="Supper club nights at The Hackney - guest chef dinners, live music and paired wines inside a restored 1860s brewery on Hackney Road. Sign up for upcoming dates.">
<!-- ==================== NAVIGATION ==================== -->
  

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 1: HERO ==================== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="Supper club dinner at The Hackney with candlelit tables and guests"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="eyebrow">Supper Club — East London E2</div>
        <h1>Guest Chef Dinners In A Restored 1860s Brewery.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Multi-course menus, paired wines, live music and no phones. A new dining series at The Hackney.</p>
        <a href="#signup" class="btn btn-primary">Get On The List</a>
        <a href="#upcoming" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-left:12px;">See Upcoming Dates</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 2: THE CONCEPT ==================== -->
  <section class="concept fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="concept-inner">
        <div class="section-label">The Concept</div>
        <h2>Dinner Without Distraction</h2>
        <p>Our supper club is a series of one-off dining events inside The Hackney — a restored 1860s brewery on Hackney Road with soaring ceilings, skylights and exposed brick.</p>
        <p>Each night features a guest chef cooking a multi-course menu, wines paired to every dish, live acoustic music and one simple rule: phones away for the evening.</p>

        <div class="concept-highlight">
          Good food. Good wine. Actual conversation. That is the whole idea.
        </div>

        <p>We are launching the series in partnership with <strong>The Nudge</strong> — London's most trusted guide to things worth doing. As we grow, we will host our own nights and invite chefs, producers and makers from across East London and beyond.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 3: UPCOMING EVENTS ==================== -->
  <section class="upcoming fade-in" id="upcoming">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Upcoming Dates</div>
      <h2>Next Supper Club</h2>
      <p class="upcoming-intro">Tickets for our current series are available through The Nudge. Sign up below to hear about future dates first.</p>

      <div class="event-cards">
        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-badge">Past Event</div>
          <div class="event-date">Wednesday 26 March 2026</div>
          <h3>Do Not Disturb: A Dopamine Reset Dinner</h3>
          <div class="event-chef">Guest Chef Ella Williams</div>
          <p class="event-desc">A phone-free evening of modern Caribbean-inspired cooking. Welcome cocktail, three courses with paired wines, and live acoustic music in a candlelit setting.</p>
          <div class="event-meta">
            <div class="event-meta-item"><strong>Price:</strong> £75pp</div>
            <div class="event-meta-item"><strong>Includes:</strong> Cocktail, 3 courses, 3 wines, live music</div>
            <div class="event-meta-item"><strong>Partner:</strong> The Nudge</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://thenudge.com/london-things-to-do/do-not-disturb-a-dopamine-reset-dinner/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">Get Tickets via The Nudge</a>
        </div>

        <!-- TEMPLATE: copy this card for future events
        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-date">DATE HERE</div>
          <h3>EVENT TITLE</h3>
          <div class="event-chef">Guest Chef NAME</div>
          <p class="event-desc">DESCRIPTION</p>
          <div class="event-meta">
            <div class="event-meta-item"><strong>Price:</strong> £XXpp</div>
            <div class="event-meta-item"><strong>Includes:</strong> DETAILS</div>
          </div>
          <a href="LINK" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">Get Tickets</a>
        </div>
        -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 4: WHAT TO EXPECT ==================== -->
  <section class="expect fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">What To Expect</div>
      <h2>How The Evening Works</h2>
      <div class="expect-grid">
        <div class="expect-item">
          <div class="expect-number">01</div>
          <h3>Arrive &amp; Unplug</h3>
          <p>You arrive at The Hackney and your phone goes into a signal-blocking pouch (you keep it on you at all times). Then it is welcome cocktails and live acoustic music in the bar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <div class="expect-number">02</div>
          <h3>Sit Down To Eat</h3>
          <p>Move through to candlelit long tables for a multi-course dinner from that evening's guest chef. Each dish is paired with a wine selected to match. Conversation flows naturally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <div class="expect-number">03</div>
          <h3>Leave Lighter</h3>
          <p>Phones come out of the pouches, you say goodbye to the people you have actually spoken to, and you head home having had a proper evening out. Post about it after — obviously.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 5: THE KITCHEN ==================== -->
  <section class="kitchen fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kitchen-inner">
        <div class="section-label">The Kitchen</div>
        <h2>Guest Chefs. In-House Kitchen.</h2>
        <p>The Hackney has its own professional kitchen led by Chef Marco Mannoni, who cooks modern European menus for our weddings and events throughout the year.</p>
        <p>For supper club nights, we invite guest chefs to take over the kitchen and bring something different — rotating styles, cuisines and stories across the series.</p>
        <p>Our first guest is Chef Ella Williams, a London-born chef whose cooking is shaped by her Jamaican heritage. Her CV includes Cafe Murano, Mountain in Soho and Hausu in Peckham. For The Hackney, she is cooking a modern Caribbean-inspired menu.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 6: GALLERY PLACEHOLDER ==================== -->
  <section class="gallery fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">The Atmosphere</div>
      <h2>An Evening At The Hackney</h2>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-block">
          <div class="gallery-block-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" style="background-color:#3D2117;"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Table</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-block">
          <div class="gallery-block-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" style="background-color:#2E4009;"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Food</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-block">
          <div class="gallery-block-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" style="background-color:#8C472E;"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Bar</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-block">
          <div class="gallery-block-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" style="background-color:#BF7256;"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">Live Music</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-block">
          <div class="gallery-block-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" style="background-color:#2C1810;"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Venue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-block">
          <div class="gallery-block-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" style="background-color:#4A3228;"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">Guests</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 7: COOK WITH US ==================== -->
  <section class="cook-with-us fade-in" id="chefs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cook-inner">
        <div class="cook-text">
          <div class="section-label">For Chefs</div>
          <h2>Cook With Us</h2>
          <p>We are building a rotating roster of guest chefs for our supper club series. If you are a chef with a story to tell through food, we want to hear from you.</p>
          <p>The Hackney has a fully equipped professional kitchen, an in-house bar team, and a dining room that seats up to 60 covers. We handle the space, the service, the drinks and the audience. You bring the menu.</p>

          <ul class="cook-what-you-get">
            <li>Professional kitchen with full extraction, gas and prep space</li>
            <li>Front-of-house and bar team provided</li>
            <li>Wine pairing handled by our team (or bring your own sommelier)</li>
            <li>Promotion to our mailing list and social channels</li>
            <li>A stunning 1860s brewery dining room with skylights and candlelight</li>
          </ul>

          <p>Whether you are running your own pop-up, launching a concept, or just want to cook for an appreciative room — get in touch.</p>

          <a href="mailto:hello@thehackney.co?subject=Supper%20Club%20Chef%20Enquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cook-image lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The Hackney professional kitchen"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 8: EMAIL SIGNUP ==================== -->
  <section class="signup fade-in" id="signup">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="signup-inner">
        <div class="section-label">Stay In The Loop</div>
        <h2>Get Supper Club Dates First</h2>
        <p>We announce new dates, guest chefs and menus by email before anywhere else. No spam — just dinner invitations a few times a year.</p>
        <form class="signup-form" id="signupForm" action="#" method="POST">
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required aria-label="Email address">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</button>
        </form>
        <p class="signup-note">We will only email you about supper club events. Unsubscribe any time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 8: CROSS-SELL ==================== -->
  <section class="cross-sell fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">More At The Hackney</div>
      <h2>Explore The Venue</h2>
      <div class="cross-sell-grid">
        <a href="/weddings/" class="cross-sell-card">
          <h3>Weddings</h3>
          <p>Exclusive hire of the entire venue for up to 60 seated guests and 100 standing. An 1860s brewery with skylights, exposed brick and an in-house kitchen.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/cafe-bar/" class="cross-sell-card">
          <h3>Cafe &amp; Bar</h3>
          <p>Speciality coffee, light bites and natural wines. Open Tuesday to Sunday — walk-ins welcome, dogs too.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== FOOTER ==================== -->
  

  <!-- ==================== JAVASCRIPT ==================== -->

<style is:global>
    /* ==================== PAGE-SPECIFIC STYLES ==================== */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 85vh;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      background: var(--brewery-dark);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      background-color: var(--brewery-dark);
      opacity: 0.45;
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      max-width: 700px;
      padding-top: 72px;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--dusty-coral);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 68px);
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    /* ==================== THE CONCEPT ==================== */
    .concept {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .concept-inner {
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .concept p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: rgba(44,24,16,0.8);
    }
    .concept-highlight {
      background: rgba(44,24,16,0.04);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--fired-brick);
      padding: 28px 32px;
      margin: 36px 0;
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 22px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ==================== UPCOMING EVENTS ==================== */
    .upcoming {
      padding: 100px 0;
      background: var(--brewery-dark);
    }
    .upcoming h2 { color: #fff; }
    .upcoming .section-label { color: var(--dusty-coral); }
    .upcoming-intro {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .event-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
      max-width: 800px;
    }
    .event-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .event-date {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--dusty-coral);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .event-card h3 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .event-chef {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .event-desc {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .event-meta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .event-meta-item {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }
    .event-meta-item strong {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .event-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 24px;
      right: 24px;
      background: var(--fired-brick);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 6px 14px;
    }

    /* ==================== WHAT TO EXPECT ==================== */
    .expect {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .expect-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 48px;
    }
    .expect-item h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .expect-item p {
      color: rgba(44,24,16,0.7);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .expect-number {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 48px;
      color: var(--dusty-coral);
      opacity: 0.4;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .expect-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    }

    /* ==================== THE KITCHEN ==================== */
    .kitchen {
      padding: 100px 0;
      background: var(--forest-olive);
    }
    .kitchen-inner {
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .kitchen .section-label { color: var(--dusty-coral); }
    .kitchen h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .kitchen p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* ==================== EMAIL SIGNUP ==================== */
    .signup {
      padding: 100px 0;
      background: var(--brewery-dark);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .signup-inner {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .signup .section-label { color: var(--dusty-coral); }
    .signup h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .signup p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .signup-form {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
    }
    .signup-form input[type="email"] {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 15px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: #fff;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .signup-form input[type="email"]::placeholder {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    }
    .signup-form input[type="email"]:focus {
      border-color: var(--dusty-coral);
    }
    .signup-form .btn-primary {
      white-space: nowrap;
      padding: 16px 28px;
    }
    .signup-note {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .signup-form { flex-direction: column; }
      .signup-form .btn-primary { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    }

    /* ==================== GALLERY PLACEHOLDER ==================== */
    .gallery {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 48px;
    }
    .gallery-block {
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .gallery-block-bg {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
    }
    .gallery-caption {
      position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(44,24,16,0.7));
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }

    /* ==================== COOK WITH US ==================== */
    .cook-with-us {
      padding: 100px 0;
      background: rgba(44,24,16,0.04);
    }
    .cook-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .cook-text h2 { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .cook-text p {
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(44,24,16,0.75);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .cook-what-you-get {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }
    .cook-what-you-get li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.08);
      font-size: 16px;
      color: rgba(44,24,16,0.8);
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .cook-what-you-get li::before {
      content: '—';
      color: var(--fired-brick);
      font-weight: 700;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .cook-image {
      aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      background: var(--forest-olive);
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .cook-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .cook-image { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
    }

    /* ==================== CROSS-SELL ==================== */
    .cross-sell {
      padding: 80px 0;
      background: rgba(44,24,16,0.04);
    }
    .cross-sell-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
      margin-top: 36px;
    }
    .cross-sell-card {
      padding: 40px;
      background: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cross-sell-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44,24,16,0.08);
    }
    .cross-sell-card h3 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .cross-sell-card p {
      color: rgba(44,24,16,0.65);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .cross-sell-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* ==================== ANIMATIONS ==================== */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    .fade-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  </style>
</Base>
